Lovely pictures. Loads of info and suggestions. Journal is a lovely idea. So far it works great and good value for money. The only improvement would be if you could go back into a journal entry to edit it. For example if you noticed a mistake or if your interpretation changed. Also, on the card of the day, I draw it in the morning but interpret it in the evening so it would be nice if they stayed together rather than being separate entries.
This deck is beautiful, and I definitely want to buy the physical version as well.
Saw this when checking out Fools Dog apps and liked the artwork. Now had some amazing readings and have ordered a real deck. Love how the app works and how beautiful the cards are.
Its fun and intriguing all at once !!! I own this actually deck of tarot cards, its very interesting as it helps me understand the meaning of the cards in a different way
